    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行按兵不动，但预测增加降息理由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/ecb-on-hold-but-forecasts-to-boost-case-for-cuts-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将在第四次会议上保持借贷成本稳定，不过新的经济预测应该会支持今年晚些时候开始降息的论据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/ecb-on-hold-but-forecasts-to-boost-case-for-cuts-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着国家寻求提振需求，中国出口增长猛增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-export-growth-jumps-in-positive-sign-for-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的出口在今年年初猛增，为世界第二大经济体应对贸易限制和地缘政治紧张局势之际的全球需求复苏发出了早期的积极信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-export-growth-jumps-in-positive-sign-for-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:07:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元随着银行股上涨而上涨，日本央行言论提振加息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/yen-gains-with-bank-stocks-as-wages-boj-remarks-lift-hike-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强劲的工资数据和央行政策制定者的言论增强了本月将取消负利率的猜测，日元攀升至一个月高位，日本银行股上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/yen-gains-with-bank-stocks-as-wages-boj-remarks-lift-hike-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:53:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国专家组推进禁令法案后，药明康德和药明生物股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/wuxi-apptec-drops-as-us-senate-panel-advances-bill-banning-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院委员会提出一项法案，该法案可能禁止中国生物技术公司获得联邦合同，并在很大程度上切断这家生物制药公司占其收入一半以上的市场的份额，导致药明康德股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/wuxi-apptec-drops-as-us-senate-panel-advances-bill-banning-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于工资超出预期，日本央行押注三月加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/japan-s-wage-growth-beats-consensus-with-fastest-pace-since-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列报告和工资数据推高日元、债券收益率和隔夜掉期之后，有关日本央行将在 3 月份采取自 2007 年以来首次加息的猜测激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/japan-s-wage-growth-beats-consensus-with-fastest-pace-since-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 23:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
